<plot>This an overlooked anime favorite for the "hentai" (perverted) "otaku" fan. It deals with two Holy Virgins, Parfait and Cacao, who are in search for through time and space, the mysterious fourth warrior. Coming along with Parfait and Cacao is an advisor named PQ, who is a small red tomato-like creature. At a space station the two Holy Virgins meet and rescue Lemon, who joins them in escaping from her captor, Ramunes the Fourth, the supposed warrior. Each episode has the catchy opening and closing theme songs.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?634749</url></doc>
